 (A)期刊論文
Chen, Ken Y., R. Elder, and Yung-Ming Hsieh, 2011, "Corporate governance, Growth Opportunities, and earnings restatements: Effect of a Corporate Governance Code", Asia Pacific Journal of Accounting and Economics [an SSCI journal], Vo. 18, No. 2, August 2011, pp. 169-200.
Chen, Ken Y., and Yung-Ming Hsieh, 2010, "Board Characteristics and Earnings Restatements: A Policy View", Journal of Financial and Economic Practice, Spring 2010 Spring 2010, pp. 55-76.
謝永明、黃荃，「會計師事務所任期與盈餘管理之關聯性—自我選擇模型之運用 (The Association between Audit Firm Tenure and Earnings Management: Evidence from the Self-Selection Model)」，會計學報 (Soochow Journal of Accounting)，第2捲第1期，2009年11月，頁73-99。
